name: SUSPICIOUS VICIOUS SPLISHY SPLASH
description: Well...that's anti-climatic...there's still one more day to 2020. See? That's how bad this book year was. Ever hear a word or a sound and think that sounds so odd, but it works? Am I the only one that thinks this? I happened to hear a track from a band called Mind Gamers, entitled "Come to America". There's a line that goes, "suspicious vicious blonde" and it just sounds so ridiculous that my partner and I were joking about it and he began to say "Suspicious vicious splishy splash." It was a fun moment that I wanted to cement into an artwork so that I will never forget it. Whether or not it's good "art" doesn't really matter. I could careless if someone hates it, it means a lot to me and that's why it's in this book. Oh and...buhhhhhh bye 2020. You were the absolute worst.
